<h1>Fippy's Facts</h1>

<a href="fippy_facts_archive.jsp">View The Fippy's Facts Archive</a>





<h2>Fippy's Epic Quest for Epic Data</h2>
<P><STRONG>Epic Weapons</STRONG></P>  <P>Fippy set out to find just how many people were heroic enough to have
  earned their epic weapons. He was startled to learn that over 80,000 people
  are happily wielding their epic in Norrath. (This is a count of actual epic
  items; in other words, if a Ranger is wielding both Swiftwind and Earthcaller
  this is counted as two epics, not one.)</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <TABLE STYLE="width:262.5pt;mso-cellspacing:.7pt;mso-padding-alt:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:0"><TD STYLE="width:60.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><STRONG>Epic Weapon</STRONG></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:20.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Class</STRONG></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:20.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Number</STRONG></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:1"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Earthcaller and Swiftwind</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Ranger</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">13,572</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:2"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Ragebringer</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Rogue</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">11,923</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:3"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Nature Walker's Scimitar</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Druid</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">11,470</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:4"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Water Sprinkler of Nem Ankh</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Cleric</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">10,736</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:5"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Celestial Fists</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Monk</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">10,481</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:6"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Blade of Tactics, Blade of Strategy, Jagged Blade of War</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Warrior</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">8,200</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:7"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Spear of Fate</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Shaman</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">7,677</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:8"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Staff of the Four</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Wizard</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">5,486</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:9"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Staff of the Serpent</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Enchanter</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">4,689</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:10"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Singing Short Sword</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Bard</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">3,674</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:11"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Orb of Mastery</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Magician</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">2,724</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:12"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Fiery Defender</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Paladin</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">2,168</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:13"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Scythe of the Shadowed Soul</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Necromancer</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">1,734</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:14"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Innoruuk's Curse</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Shadowknight</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">1,232</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:15"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Claw of the Savage Spirit</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Beastlord</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">1,106</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:16;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">&nbsp;</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>TOTAL</STRONG></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">81,275</P></TD></TR></TABLE>  <P><BR>&nbsp;</P>  <P>The Ranger epic consists of two different swords.&nbsp;
  Fippy broke down the data for each of these, too:</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <TABLE STYLE="width:262.5pt;mso-cellspacing:.7pt;mso-padding-alt:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:0"><TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><STRONG>Epic Weapon</STRONG></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:15.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Number</STRONG></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:35.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Notes</STRONG></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:1"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Swiftwind</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">8,802</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">A secondary weapon</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:2"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Earthcaller</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">4,770</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">A primary weapon</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:3;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Both epic swords in use</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">4,757</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">---</P></TD></TR></TABLE>  <P><BR>&nbsp;</P>  <P>The Warrior epic is even more complicated, consisting of
  two separate and usable swords, which can be combined to create a single new
  epic:</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <TABLE STYLE="width:262.5pt;mso-cellspacing:.7pt;mso-padding-alt:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:0"><TD STYLE="width:35.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><STRONG>Epic Weapon</STRONG></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:15.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Number</STRONG></P></TD>    <TD STYLE="width:50.0%;padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center"><STRONG>Notes</STRONG></P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:1"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Blade of Strategy</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">3,287</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">A secondary weapon</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:2"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Blade of Tactics</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">3,264</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">A primary weapon</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:3"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Jagged Blade of War</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">1,649</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">The combined epic</P></TD></TR>   <TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:4;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt">Both lesser swords</TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">2,204</P></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><P ALIGN="center">Swords used independently</P></TD></TR></TABLE>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <P>Finally, Fippy just had to know which servers were the <STRONG>most
  epic</STRONG>, so he ran around counting all the epics on every server!</P>  <P>&nbsp;</P>  <TABLE STYLE="mso-cellspacing:.7pt;mso-padding-alt:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"><TR STYLE="mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-lastrow:yes"><TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"></TD>    <TD STYLE="padding:5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt 5.25pt"></TD></TR></TABLE>  <P>Well done <STRONG>Veeshan</STRONG> and <STRONG>Tunare</STRONG>! The fact
  that Fippy himself plays on Veeshan is entirely a coincidence.</P>  <P>(Data gathered: December 2002)</P>



